{"tid":923198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屈穎妍:聖經充滿愛與和平","createTime":"2018-12-01T05:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T11:19:27.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9553fb5df3ed6d49e0ff993b4c1f772b57b28a","tid":923198,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95/40164/-%E4%BD%A0%E8%AE%80%E7%9A%84-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BD%E8%81%96%E7%B6%93-?fbclid=IwAR2iZUZTRtQg1mbaad6HJ5zNOLBQ-2kBlzMVJnG3dhJJdUxfaluUBRU4hOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%25A9%2595%2F40164%2F-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%25AE%2580%25E7%259A%2584-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BD%25E8%2581%2596%25E7%25B6%2593-%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2iZUZTRtQg1mbaad6HJ5zNOLBQ-2kBlzMVJnG3dhJJdUxfaluUBRU4hOo&d=IGUMcHggKeeOZ9hQ12bYrUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=bf2c9e10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95/40164/-%E4%BD%A0%E8%AE%80%E7%9A%84-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BD%E8%81%96%E7%B6%93-?fbclid=IwAR2iZUZTRtQg1mbaad6HJ5zNOLBQ-2kBlzMVJnG3dhJJdUxfaluUBRU4hOo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我不是教徒，對聖經也只是略知皮毛</span>，但這些年，我對信仰的疑問特別多，那天碰巧跟一位基督教朋友聊天，於是乘機請教：<br />\n<br />\n「耶穌說，要愛你的仇敵。好明顯，共產黨是朱耀明牧師、陳日君樞機、戴耀廷李柱銘黎智英等教徒的仇敵，請問，為什麼他們不愛她？」<br />\n<br />\n我完全沒有挑戰宗教的意思，這疑問，一直在我腦海縈繞多年。<br />\n<br />\n一班挑動社會暴力、社會仇恨的領頭人，竟有不少是虔誠教徒、甚至教會主事者，<span style=\"color: red;\">我年輕時也讀過聖經上過教會，明明聽的看的都是愛與寬恕，但這些年看佔中的主腦，卻一直用暴力仇恨來演繹教義，我實在大惑不解。</span><br />\n<br />\n公民黨大狀吳靄儀早前寫了篇文章叫「耶穌的暴力」，竟然以耶穌來比喻煽動暴亂而被判囚的梁天琦：「耶穌和他的門徒來到耶路撒冷度逾越節，見聖殿處處擺滿販賣檔攤及找換貨幣的商人，牛羊混雜，烏煙瘴氣，他拿起繩索為鞭子把他們驅逐出去，怒斥他們，這是他父的聖殿，這些人卻將之變成強盜窩。」<br />\n<br />\n吳靄儀說，耶穌使用了暴力，卻沒被控普通襲擊、非法集結甚至暴動罪，二千幾年來「亦無人指出耶穌非法行使暴力」，言下之意，梁天琦也不該被判罪！<br />\n<br />\n聖經是這樣解讀的嗎？我真的給弄糊塗了。<br />\n<br />\n於是我再問道於另一位基督徒朋友，她告訴我：「神的國不在地上，<span style=\"color: red;\">耶穌的年代掌權者也有問題，但衪沒有去推翻他</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n同一本聖經，落在不同人手上，原來可以如此天南地北。<br />\n<br />\n又有基督徒說，因為內地禁基督教拆十字架，所以他們要對抗這「暴政」，我奇怪，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果因為別人不相信你就推翻他，這世上何必有傳道人？</span><br />\n<br />\n這幾天的佔中審訊一直聽那些暴力倡導者又在說愛與和平，我想起朱耀明牧師早前在一個教協講座中這兩句話：「社會上很多人沒教人如何做人，卻只教人愛國愛港！」<span style=\"color: red;\">愛自己國家愛自己土地都是錯？到底朱牧師讀的是什麽聖經？</span><br />\n<br />\n經聖教世人愛國愛黨，和理非非，絕對唔可以推翻現世政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b19a50f9d812951af519ee11b4e5491c3fa3597","tid":923198,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"去死啦 垃圾"},{"pid":"4761b659e0a682dddc5f72bc4d9e88903d1f6f6f","tid":923198,"uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「神的國不在地上，耶穌的年代掌權者也有問題，但衪沒有去推翻他。」</span><br />\n<br />\n個陣時啲以色列王波斯王羅馬王去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又知唔係神推翻佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112d44d15eae5953e16be33217a74b9c0bc9bd9f","tid":923198,"uid":204985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"講到咁好又唔去信教"},{"pid":"4ad1715f4c98657d6d60abefcf634ae84900f303","tid":923198,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4761b659e0a682dddc5f72bc4d9e88903d1f6f6f","tid":923198,"uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「神的國不在地上，耶穌的年代掌權者也有問題，但衪沒有去推翻他。」</span><br />\n<br />\n個陣時啲以色列王波斯王羅馬王去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又知唔係神推翻佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"又係喎小學D聖經故事次次以色列人比異族欺壓時，上主就會派出先知去推翻佢地，跟住以色列人繼續拜金牛，無限loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2efd7460b61c393413c0389829570118c9a1f9","tid":923198,"uid":48362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"亂倫同殺人個d又點計呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184579587d094d730c823a67e84a8b37b92ac193","tid":923198,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca2efd7460b61c393413c0389829570118c9a1f9","tid":923198,"uid":48362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"亂倫同殺人個d又點計呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"犯曬十戒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbbf1d9084aa6067621e28d1acd91f618b0f208","tid":923198,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"人地係天主教徒 支持統治者係基督教嘅嘢"},{"pid":"f53e3a7024306799fd21069db9b010382e4721fe","tid":923198,"uid":90577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"聖經入面殺得最多人既就係上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9634b76d4f9c6c9ab6ecc9e69877c93b4b28b280","tid":923198,"uid":140041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"fon